---
title: "Update Devices"
api: "POST /api/devices"
authMethod: none
openapi: "/openapi-specs/Roomi Devices.json POST /api/devices"
---

Update device settings and control states for multiple devices.

## Headers


| Name | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Authorization | Yes | AWS4-HMAC-SHA256 signature |
| X-Amz-Content-Sha256 | Yes | SHA256 hash of the request body |
| X-Amz-Date | Yes | ISO8601 timestamp |
| X-Unit-ID | Yes | Unit identifier |
| X-User-ID | Yes | User identifier |


## Body

```json
{
  "user_id": "user-123",
  "unit_id": "unit-456",
  "data": {
    "devices": [
      {
        "deviceId": "device-456",
        "targetValue": "100",
        "actionType": "set_brightness",
        "actionId": 1
      }
    ]
  }
}
```
